author: Chris Danforth
title: The 10 Most Expensive Sneakers at Sneaker Con Phoenix SS17
text:
Visit the original post to see all 10 images from this gallery. 
We already showed you our favorite 15 on-foot looks from Sneaker Con Phoenix – now we address the main event.
We hit the shelves to recap the most expensive pairs from the event, which included a number of rare Jordans and of course some Kanye West-designed goods. An unreleased, sample pair of Jordan 29s took the silver medal in Phoenix, while the crazy rare Undefeated x Air Jordan 4 took that number one spot.
Check out the full list below, then browse through our gallery above.
What did you pick up at #SneakerCon Phoenix? 
A post shared by Sneaker Con (@sneakercon) on Mar 18, 2017 at 10:22pm PDT 

1. Undefeated x Air Jordan 4 – $15,000 
2. Air Jordan 29 “Oregon” (Sample) – $6,000 
3. Nike Air Yeezy 2 SP “Red October” – $4,000 
4. Louis Vuitton X Kanye West “Don C” – $3,200 
5. Air Jordan 12 “Melo” P.E. – $3,000 
6. Kanye West x Reebok “S.Carter” – $2,000 
7. Nike Air Yeezy 2 NRG “Pure Platinum” – $1,800 
8. Air Jordan 9 PRM “BIN23” – $1,700 
9. fragment design x Air Jordan 1 – $1,600 
10. Air Jordan 4 “Doernbecher” – $1,400
